  "remarks": "An armed group in eastern Ukraine. Part of the so-called ‘1st Army Corps’ of the ‘People's Republic of Donetsk’. In November 2017, the unit was named in honour of the assassinated separatist military commander Arsen Pavlov (aka Motorola).; Listing: Listed on 1 Sep. 2017 (relisted on 28 Aug. 2020) (relisted on 27 Aug 2023)",
